Here’s a better look at all 10 Formula 1 teams as Outfits! 
.
Honestly it’s not my best work, it was very rushed just so I could post the reel just at time of the season opener. Can I do better? Yes! But I am somewhat happy with the job I did in the timeframe I had…making sure the colour proportions match the car liveries and the design language took the most Time, not to mention we shot, edit & uploaded the reel in just 24hrs!! Next time I’ll do better and make sure I have more time in hand 👍🏼

latestPosts.caption:
Nanu I am finally on @forbesindia 🥹, I am out of words & full of emotions, what a way to turn 22 years old this month 🤩, this journey had its ups and downs, what I started as just a money grab project has turned into a passion project & something that I just love doing. Never thought I would be here when I started all this in 2018. 

To all the people who doubted me, called me names, made fun of me for trying, I know you all and I remember your names and faces, you are one of the reasons why I’m here so appreciate that 🤝🏼

I want to thank you all, each and every single one of you who is a part of this family of ours for supporting me through out this journey, I am grateful for all the comments, all jokes, all the compliments, all the wishes literally everything!! I genuinely appreciate that, I love you all ❤️

Thank you for making this dream come true 😇

Also big big thanks to my team @yinyangcreatives.in that has also been there when I make stupid mistakes. @projectatusha & @whatkcdoes thank you for believing in me & just guiding me when I didn’t know what to do, @_soniyayayaa really sorry for responding late to calls and messages, also for having my back when I delay things 🫡😂

And @_ayush.h my best buddy who was the person I started this journey with & @im_ajay_shanker for always showing up at 3pm for a random photoshoot & my special one, thank you all 3 of you for being on my side when no one was, I owe you a big one ❤️

Got a new Watch ⌚️‼️ The new Argos Olympus, do you like the watch!?
.
A lot of guys were asking me to check out @argoswatch , so I finally got my hands on the Argos Olympus which India’s first watch with a power reserve indicator✨, it’s also specs loaded with an automatic movement, sapphire crystal, & exhibition case it has to be one the best watches under budget of 15k, the dial, the finishes & the solid link bracelet is unheard of at this price point.
.
